milestones.description: Ashish Bagai and Dhaniram's 109-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 96 between Ashif Mulla and Abdool Samad
Noor Ali and Shahzad's 205-run partnership is AFG's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 79 between Asghar Afghan and Shahzad
Shahzad's 118 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for AFG), surpassing Shahzad's 110
Shahzad has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (56) in an innings in ODIs for AFG, going past Shahzad's 44
Noor Ali and Shahzad's 205-run partnership is AFG's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 86 between Raees and Samiullah Shinwari
Asghar Afghan has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (4) for AFG, going past Hamid Hassan
Shahzad has scored 2 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for AFG breaking Mohammad Nabi's record
